                    "text": {
                      "value": "<b>The common goal of Rolex and SKAI (a major Greek TV channel), to contribute and improve humanity and the planet, led to SKAI's series of exclusive documentaries, produced in partnership with Rolex. </b>\n<br/><br/>\n\n“The Pioneers who shape the future” is a series of eight documentaries, 3 minutes duration each, presenting the stories of exceptional men and women who have a spirit of enterprise, initiating extraordinary projects that improve life on the planet, expand knowledge, or preserve our natural and cultural heritage.\n"
                    },
